                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "heightened",
                "level": 7,
                "text": "On a failure, the target is controlled for 1 round. On a critical failure, the target is controlled for up to 1 minute; it receives a new Will save at the end of each of its turns, and on a success, the spell ends."
